{"tid":1015152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍步兵將配備微型偵察機 可放進口袋裡","createTime":"2019-02-09T17:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T08:44:01.000Z","uid":141151,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"df415380223cea5de457ccbe68b65f5136a7751d","tid":1015152,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T17:16:17.000Z","msg":"美軍步兵將配備微型偵察機 可放進口袋裡<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/19/2/8/n11031966.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F19%2F2%2F8%2Fn11031966.htm&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BP2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=f6529f96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/19/2/8/n11031966.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n【大紀元2019年02月08日訊】（大紀元記者陳俊村編譯報導）美國陸軍已經採購一種可執行偵察任務的微型無人機，預計今年配發給步兵單位的士兵，以期協助士兵作戰並減少人員死傷。這種無人機只有十幾公分長，可以放進口袋裡，攜帶十分方便。<br />\n<br />\n這種名為黑黃蜂個人偵察系統（Black Hornet Personal Reconnaissance System）的迷你無人機由FLIR系統公司（Flir Systems）所生產，美國陸軍已經與該公司簽訂高達3,960萬美元的採購合約。<br />\n<br />\n本次合作源自於美軍的「軍人隨身感應器」（Soldier Borne Sensor, SBS）計劃。早在去年6月，美國陸軍已經為第一批這種無人機與FLIR系統公司簽訂第一階段的合約。<br />\n<br />\n這種無人機的重量為1.16盎司（32.9公克），長度只有大約6英寸（15.2公分），小到可以放在口袋裡。它可以在幾乎無聲的情況下飛行25分鐘，所以很適合飛到敵人陣地協助士兵偵察敵情。<br />\n<br />\n該無人機在日夜間均可操作，它可飛行長達1.24英里（2公里）的距離，並以每秒20英尺（6.1公尺）的最高速度巡視地面情況，再將攝影機拍攝到的即時影像和高清照片傳回給使用者。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">陸軍發言人泰勒（Isaac Taylor）告訴「任務與目的」（Task &amp; Purpose）網站說，這款裝備將藉由其蒐集情報、進行監視和偵察的能力，讓各班的士兵立即了解戰場上的情況。<br />\n<br />\nFLIR系統公司則表示，此無人機秘密偵測並辨識威脅的能力，可以在戰場上拯救士兵的性命。<br />\n<br />\n該公司執行長加農（Jim Cannon）在一份聲明中說：「這項合約代表奈米無人機（nano-UAV）在世界最強大的陸軍進行大規模作戰部署的一個重要里程碑。」</span><br />\n<br />\n該聲明稱，這種無人機<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">預計在2019年稍早開始交貨。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n泰勒指出，黑黃蜂個人偵察系統將先配發到一個旅級戰鬥隊（brigade combat team），隨後再配發到陸軍的其它35個旅級戰鬥隊。#"},{"pid":"c14da6c71e662e2e3ba0e553f0d7ec055cf858cb","tid":1015152,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T17:18:38.000Z","msg":"幾乎無聲的情況下飛行25分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0955ce5c9b3d792b68a9c5608e6d48a140b51711","tid":1015152,"uid":10757,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T17:21:47.000Z","msg":"battlefield<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04610166c4ebc1ee005284fe0f45734919f3282c","tid":1015152,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T17:24:56.000Z","msg":"2019交貨<br />\n即將係測試左10年以上"},{"pid":"d59ad3e7e26c7a84ec81685ec140528573af592e","tid":1015152,"uid":23162,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T17:55:54.000Z","msg":"怕你有毛，中國都有DJI,都唔知幾多港豬吹奏<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3583afe2ec849c69f44ffcb9e2f8a5613f52474a","tid":1015152,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T01:35:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"23375067dd195c3bc5ad2dc9f76cae532c3c6c7a","tid":1015152,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T01:59:33.000Z","msg":"五毛又話美軍對dji欲擺不能既？"},{"pid":"c182afb6423fd271c49f494ee97888ed5b5e8f59","tid":1015152,"uid":141151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"3583afe2ec849c69f44ffcb9e2f8a5613f52474a","tid":1015152,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T01:35:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T02:29:27.000Z","msg":"你有能力將核彈縮細到呢個程度<br />\n暗殺總統、主席都得添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"h